content:
Wilderness Rune Mine may refer to:

  • Lava Maze runite mine, a mine famously known as Wilderness Rune Mine that is located north-west of the Lava Maze in level 46 Wilderness containing two runite rocks.
  • Lava Maze Dungeon mine, inside the Lava Maze Dungeon with a single rune rock.
  • Frozen Waste Plateau, located in the north-west corner of the Wilderness with several rune rocks.
 This page is used to distinguish between articles with similar names.

'''Wilderness Rune Mine''' may refer to:
*[[Lava Maze runite mine]], a [[mine]] famously known as '''Wilderness Rune Mine''' that is located north-west of the [[Lava Maze]] in level 46 [[Wilderness]] containing two [[runite rock]]s.
*[[Lava Maze Dungeon mine]], inside the [[Lava Maze Dungeon]] with a single rune rock.
*[[Frozen Waste Plateau]], located in the north-west corner of the Wilderness with several rune rocks.
